				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">AE song Agro in Raid<a name="26168"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 8 04 12:31 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>last weekend, i was on a Mithaniel Marr raid with 2 other bards. i was the MT bard so i sing DS, haste, PoV, and amp.
<br />
The other bard said that he has to go long afk and will auto follow on his group mate while singin AE regen non-stop. the other bard, not too high level decide that he should sing AE Resist song non stop. well basically their song covers the whole raider (+/- 80peps). 
<br />

<br />
until we start pulling dogs. 
<br />
the AFK bard died instantly before the MT can do anything. 
<br />
the resist singer bard died right after the afk bard. Those dogs then bites me for ... 99% hp in less than 1 sec. lucky i had FM and run. 
<br />

<br />
the resist singer bard then get rezzed, and start singing resist again. bad move. dogs ate him again. i was busy singing MT buff didnt even get any hit. the afk bard..god bless his soul..never get rezzed until nearly the end of the raid.
<br />

<br />

<br />
so.. watch out when you singing AE song. the agro is HUGE. even smelly ogre tank cant taunt fast enough. FM is your friend. and dont go AFK while singin AE in raid.
<br />

<br />
Bombom
<br />
</span></td>
